{"tid":1246411,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[武打科幻警匪] 張晉新戲《九龍不敗》值唔值得支持？","createTime":"2019-06-20T16:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T01:51:12.000Z","uid":15213,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d76e8af0d836e8625e4030330d89a370340dce13","tid":1246411,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"今日張晉新戲上，有冇人睇咗？會唔會睇？<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 張晉 vs. UFC拳王Anderson Silva <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳果導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">《九龍不敗》</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://wmoov.com/assets/movie/photo/201905/60197197_10156478736337756_3390361009238573056_o_1557333431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwmoov.com%2Fassets%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201905%2F60197197_10156478736337756_3390361009238573056_o_1557333431.jpg&h=dcbb0af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">簡介：</span></span><br />\n警探九龍(張晉飾) 身上的龍紋身，記錄著他兒時一段疑真疑假的經歷 ，查案時瘋狂併搏；在奉命調查一宗女警連環被殺案時，九龍用盡方法不僅毫無線索， 他的警花未婚妻方寧（鄧麗欣飾）也在這場拘捕行動中意外失踪。九龍發現女警連環遇害只是第一步，兇手還有著更加血腥的陰謀，自己和未婚妻竟然也被算計其中；此時澳門再度發生女警被殺案，這次的作案手法更加令人髮指，但兇手好像故意留下線索，是危險陷阱還是複仇曙光？九龍為追真兇，不惜跨境調查，但屢被澳門警司曹志德（鄭嘉穎飾）刻意阻撓，最後在好友澳門大小姐王夢奇（劉心悠飾）協助，發現案件竟與前美國黑人陸戰隊員、曾於拳賽敗給九龍的冼力山（Anderson Silva飾）有關。 魔高一丈，道高幾何！血債血償之前，就算流乾最後一滴血，九龍也要誓不罷休。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">演員：</span></span><br />\n張晉、Anderson Silva、鄭嘉穎、劉心悠、鄧麗欣、周國賢、陳鈺芸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">預告：</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oT1nl5NfWWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoT1nl5NfWWY&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranpIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=8d55f20f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oT1nl5NfWWY</a>"},{"pid":"6b2d6dd959bb751dec46880f4cf14671030a7aa1","tid":1246411,"uid":48295,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"陳果不了 張晉不了"},{"pid":"0d18588185a79f6cc78c7fbf0d9966ef367f3257","tid":1246411,"uid":54232,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"起碼睇三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6759d3e099ff0d935b32b438edec5677edcbc97","tid":1246411,"uid":257182,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:01:28.000Z","msg":"黃百嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不了"},{"pid":"8edc4fe1e03e055aa0a8f3e1cd1840daa1b16d3a","tid":1246411,"uid":78385,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"e6759d3e099ff0d935b32b438edec5677edcbc97","tid":1246411,"uid":257182,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:01:28.000Z","msg":"黃百嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"黃百嗚 nono"},{"pid":"8b1e6b543d151edaf2fdbcdf09b6661bd7f95a6b","tid":1246411,"uid":7206,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:12:43.000Z","msg":"香港差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fbb7ebe2bf8768b14a74a359788976971bf764","tid":1246411,"uid":15213,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"呢度唔係好多人鍾意睇唔用腦動作片咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ece737d72734f4bedbe71dd27405788a686dd54","tid":1246411,"uid":238673,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"睇咗。"},{"pid":"1cc4d1624ba1b7c416d1e2cc9ca092fd8eb2c369","tid":1246411,"uid":75935,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"睇左 好撚垃